## Content Strategy

### The Mix

- **70% Craft & Expertise** — product decisions, business impact stories, cross-functional work, process reveals, takes on product and design trends. This builds the reputation that makes the right people reach out.
- **15% Personal / Behind the work** — career moments, the decision that looked wrong at first, honest observations about what the job actually is. Humanizes without dominating.
- **15% Conversion** — job-search posts, consulting offers, direct asks. Done right.

### Post Types

| Type | Goal | Frequency |
|------|------|-----------|
| **Authority** | Build credibility with target audience | 2 of every 3 posts |
| **Visibility** | Reach new people, grow following | 1 of every 3 posts |
| **Conversion** | Direct ask — job lead, client inquiry | Max 1× per 2 weeks |

