## Hook Examples

```
Increased trial-to-paid conversion by 22%.
We changed when the value appeared, not what the UI looked like.
```

```
The PM wanted to add a feature. The research said remove one.
We removed it.
Retention went up the next quarter.
```

```
Most design systems don't fail because of the design.
They fail because nobody owned what happened after they shipped it.
```

